Meta-layer containing only the Neutrino recipes (neutrino-mp, libstb-hal,
plugins, themes) for Tuxbox-OS on OE-Alliance platforms.

Notes
-----
- Yocto release: Kirkstone (4.0 LTS)
- Only Neutrino-specific recipes live here; all generic distro, middleware,
  connectivity, toolchain, firmware, Qt/Kodi and miscellaneous support recipes
  were moved to `meta-tuxbox`.
- Classes, licenses and waf cross-answers are now provided by `meta-tuxbox`.

Usage
-----
Add both layers to `bblayers.conf`:

    BBLAYERS += "/path/to/meta-neutrino /path/to/meta-tuxbox"

